					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3290299#post-4417309</guid>
				<title>Do you think making me cry is cool?</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3290299/the-little-robot-that-could#post-4417309</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2019 12:47:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Slipperysilas</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4729184</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&quot;They'd been gone for so long though. What if, just what if, they weren't coming back? Well, he had the bacteria, right? But could he talk to the bacteria? Could he have friendly conversations with the bacteria? Could he even be friends with the bacteria?&quot;</p> <p>My guy this just makes my heart hurt. I hope someday, someone makes it to his party.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
